CARR, Respondent, v. CARR, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Otis N. Carr against Charles D. Carr.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Motion to dismiss appeal on the ground of the nonservice of papers granted, without costs to either party.
